    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/946701f1d9c28c32c257c5bbe956b5b5.poster.avif?t=1768738003\" width=1118 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/946701f1d9c28c32c257c5bbe956b5b5.webm?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/946701f1d9c28c32c257c5bbe956b5b5.mp4?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">🦀🎸🎵</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">1. <strong>组建可爱蟹蟹乐队（自定义现场音乐 &amp; 构筑独特能力）</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">从摇滚、爵士、放克、国风、管弦乐到电子合成，任意组合你的乐队蟹蟹。无论是二胡配DJ，还是架子鼓配萨克斯风，皆由你来定义！每一种搭配都会创造出独一无二的实时音乐！从中华武术乐队，到高科技无人机黑客乐队，再到可爱的少女偶像蟹蟹乐队，数不清的独特乐队等待你去发现，每位音乐蟹蟹都有专属的能力与风格。<strong>组建你的乐队，同时塑造你的构筑！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/fe75d4d3dfa17d0d9a3051634253e01c.poster.avif?t=1768738003\" width=958 height=516 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/fe75d4d3dfa17d0d9a3051634253e01c.webm?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/fe75d4d3dfa17d0d9a3051634253e01c.mp4?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/b307643dc2b4248cd3e90f70489da469.poster.avif?t=1768738003\" width=1118 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/b307643dc2b4248cd3e90f70489da469.webm?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/b307643dc2b4248cd3e90f70489da469.mp4?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">🦀🎸🎵</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">2. <strong>独特的可强化音乐武器（多样机制 &amp; 爽快战斗）</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">从 <strong>竹笛矛 </strong>到 <strong>小号霰弹枪</strong>，从 <strong>吉他电锯</strong> 到 <strong>贝斯机枪</strong>，从 <strong>太极鼓珠</strong> 到 <strong>古筝风刃</strong>，以及更多令人期待的惊喜——科技巨头 <strong>钳音堂 (Claw House)</strong> 为玩家提供了海量强力且独一无二的音乐武器，并通过<strong>快递空投 (Delivery Drop)</strong> 服务送货上门！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/b0a0ccf9f4cd84974d75917c1d8c2281.poster.avif?t=1768738003\" width=950 height=510 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/b0a0ccf9f4cd84974d75917c1d8c2281.webm?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/b0a0ccf9f4cd84974d75917c1d8c2281.mp4?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/f0e68e7c3afd8cfaf77a379321591bbc.poster.avif?t=1768738003\" width=950 height=510 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/f0e68e7c3afd8cfaf77a379321591bbc.webm?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/f0e68e7c3afd8cfaf77a379321591bbc.mp4?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/a920c8a79e9eafe3008f9d82f2c7ceff.poster.avif?t=1768738003\" width=1118 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/a920c8a79e9eafe3008f9d82f2c7ceff.webm?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/a920c8a79e9eafe3008f9d82f2c7ceff.mp4?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">🦀🎸🎵</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>3. 使用钳钳芯片随时构筑强化（整合强化 &amp; 策略构筑）</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">通过 <strong>钳钳手表 (Claw Watch)</strong>，玩家可以随时进入 <strong>钳钳芯片商店 (Claw Chip Store)</strong> 购买各类独特的芯片，获取全新的能力。凭借这些灵活多变的芯片，每一次冒险都能根据你的偏好而塑造——无论是更偏策略，还是更偏动作！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/b4798daed135197247036e051dfcfd14.poster.avif?t=1768738003\" width=958 height=516 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/b4798daed135197247036e051dfcfd14.webm?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/b4798daed135197247036e051dfcfd14.mp4?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/9a81e2e05a853879171da4c7f0e5904d.poster.avif?t=1768738003\" width=958 height=516 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/9a81e2e05a853879171da4c7f0e5904d.webm?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/9a81e2e05a853879171da4c7f0e5904d.mp4?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/11f7d9a924a3463afd75d826df50e6ca.poster.avif?t=1768738003\" width=1118 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/11f7d9a924a3463afd75d826df50e6ca.webm?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/11f7d9a924a3463afd75d826df50e6ca.mp4?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">🦀🎸🎵</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>4. 打扮漂亮，选择你的蟹蟹今日穿搭! </strong>(能力装扮)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">自定义开局能力装扮，改变蟹蟹的可爱呆傻形象并为接下来的游戏提供特殊的能力效果。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/0764ae7d0d6fbdd34c3db83eeda91c12.poster.avif?t=1768738003\" width=1000 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/0764ae7d0d6fbdd34c3db83eeda91c12.webm?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402540/extras/0764ae7d0d6fbdd34c3db83eeda91c12.mp4?t=1768738003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
